        public void serialize(LittleEndianOutput out)
        Description copied from class: StandardRecord
        Write the data content of this BIFF record. The 'ushort sid' and 'ushort size' header fields have already been written by the superclass.

        The number of bytes written must equal the record size reported by RecordBase.getRecordSize()} minus four ( record header consisting of a 'ushort sid' and 'ushort reclength' has already been written by their superclass).

        (写入此BIFF记录的数据内容。超类已经编写了“ushort sid”和“ushort size”标头字段。写入的字节数必须等于RecordBase报告的记录大小。getRecordSize（）}减四（由“ushort sid”和“ushort reclong”组成的记录头已由其超类写入）。)

      • getColor

        public byte[] getColor(int byteIndex)
        Returns the color value at a given index(返回给定索引处的颜色值)
        Parameters:
        byteIndex - palette index, must be >= 0x8(byteIndex -调色板索引，必须>= 0x 8)
        Returns:
        the RGB triplet for the color, or null if the specified index does not exist(颜色的三重组，如果指定的索引不存在，则为空)

      • setColor

        public void setColor(short byteIndex,
                     byte red,
                     byte green,
                     byte blue)
        Sets the color value at a given index If the given index is greater than the current last color index, then black is inserted at every index required to make the palette continuous.(在给定索引处设置颜色值如果给定索引大于当前最后一个颜色索引，则在使调色板连续所需的每个索引处插入黑色。)
        Parameters:
        byteIndex - the index to set; if this index is less than 0x8 or greater than 0x40, then no modification is made(byteIndex -要设置的索引;如果该索引小于0x 8或大于0x 40，则不进行修改)
        red - the red color part(红色-红色部分)
        green - the green color part(绿色-绿色部分)
        blue - the blue color part(蓝色-蓝色部分)
